# The trunk-emitted bundle is *generated* by `trunk build --release`
# inside the container builder stage, so any host-side `dist/` is
# stale at best and lockfile-poisoning at worst. Strip it from the
# build context, but keep the `.gitkeep` placeholder so the empty
# directory is created (include_dir! refuses a missing path; trunk
# itself prefers to populate an existing dir).
